 when"," it"," is"," safe"," to"," do"," so",".","\n\n","It"," is"," important"," to"," prioritize"," safety"," over"," the"," urge"," to"," use"," a"," cell"," phone"," while"," driving","."," While"," it"," may"," be"," tempting"," to"," answer"," a"," call"," or"," respond"," to"," a"," text"," message",","," it"," is"," crucial"," to"," remember"," that"," doing"," so"," can"," wait","."," Drivers"," should"," remind"," themselves"," that"," their"," safety"," and"," the"," safety"," of"," others"," on"," the"," road"," is"," more"," important"," than"," a"," phone"," call"," or"," text"," message",".","\n\n","In"," addition"," to"," the"," strategies"," mentioned"," above",","," there"," are"," other"," ways"," to"," reduce"," the"," temptation"," to"," use"," a"," cell"," phone"," while"," driving","."," Drivers"," can"," put"," their"," phone"," in"," a"," place"," where"," it"," is"," not"," easily"," accessible",","," such"," as"," the"," glove"," compartment"," or"," trunk","."," They"," can"," also"," use"," apps"," that"," block"," notifications"," while"," driving"," or"," that"," require"," them"," to"," pass"," a"," test"," to"," prove"," they"," are"," not"," driving"," before"," allowing"," them"," to"," use"," their"," phone",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," using"," a"," cell"," phone"," while"," driving"," is"," a"," dangerous"," and"," potentially"," deadly"," habit","."," It"," can"," lead"," to"," accidents",","," injuries",","," and"," fatalities",","," as"," well"," as"," legal"," and"," financial"," consequences"," for"," the"," driver","."," To"," avoid"," using"," a"," cell"," phone"," while"," driving",","," drivers"," can"," connect"," to"," Bluetooth"," or"," put"," their"," phone"," on"," do"," not"," disturb","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," prioritize"," safety"," over"," the"," urge"," to"," use"," a"," cell"," phone"," while"," driving",","," and"," to"," remember"," that"," the"," safety"," of"," themselves"," and"," other